org.kymjs.kjframe.plugin

Interface I_CJActivity

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CJActivity

    public interface I_CJActivity
    CJFrameActivity接口协议，插件Activity必须实现此接口
    Activity实现此接口意味着将插件的Activity生命周期交給CJFrame托管， 而不再是ActivityManager托管
    创建时间 2014-10-11
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    kymjs (https://github.com/kymjs)
